data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="312">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$pei-zhi-xin" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/pei-zhi-xin" class="zg-link" title="裴志信">裴志信</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jiang-ke-chao-24" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jiang-ke-chao-24" class="zg-link" title="蒋可超">蒋可超</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-zhe-miao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-zhe-miao" class="zg-link" title="Caster喵">Caster喵</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2888859" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">电影和电影的质感是不一样的。<br><br>以100块哥这张照片为例。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/d4113b9f3aa41992bb551eff872caf7a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image" width="247"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image lazy" width="247" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/d4113b9f3aa41992bb551eff872caf7a_b.jpg"><br><br>色相/饱和度，把除了红色以外的颜色饱和度都降到最低。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/3e771180aa6fd1ca84ca938f57a0d7fc_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="873" data-rawheight="570" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="873" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/3e771180aa6fd1ca84ca938f57a0d7fc_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="873" data-rawheight="570" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="873" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/3e771180aa6fd1ca84ca938f57a0d7fc_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/3e771180aa6fd1ca84ca938f57a0d7fc_b.jpg"><br>这是《辛德勒名单》的质感。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/158f3b302a68d223ea27b7f1f688afe8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image" width="247"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image lazy" width="247" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/158f3b302a68d223ea27b7f1f688afe8_b.jpg"><br><br>把绿色曲线推高，然后给角色带上墨镜，再把背景换成数字瀑布。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/719435ba22c4ade91044d564c963e857_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="832" data-rawheight="571" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="832" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/719435ba22c4ade91044d564c963e857_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="832" data-rawheight="571" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="832" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/719435ba22c4ade91044d564c963e857_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/719435ba22c4ade91044d564c963e857_b.jpg"><br>这是《黑客帝国》的质感。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/85c5c5a6f424efa7baaf9c2cefd71e4e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image" width="247"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image lazy" width="247" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/85c5c5a6f424efa7baaf9c2cefd71e4e_b.jpg"><br><br>增加曝光度，降低饱和度，找个地方写上“Tokyo Hot”。<br><br><br>这是Tokyo Hot质感。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/9a21b9e7505b9db56e836316f6b2a6a3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image" width="247"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="247" data-rawheight="441" class="content_image lazy" width="247" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/9a21b9e7505b9db56e836316f6b2a6a3_b.jpg">


</div>

</div>
